Day 14: Foster Team Ownership!
🎯 "When the team owns the process, they own the success!"  
👉 Tip: Encourage your team to take full ownership of their sprint commitments. Empowerment breeds accountability.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
-----

🧠 Poll: "How much ownership does your team take in sprint planning and commitments?"  
1. Full ownership 🚀  
2. Mostly accountable 🏗️  
3. Could be better 🔧  
4. Not much ownership 🛑
